clear
cat <<'BANNER'
============================================================
   ___  ___ ___  ___ ___ ___  _   _
  / _ \|_ _/ _ \/ __/ __| _ \| | | |
 | (_) || || (_) \__ \__ \  _/ |_| |
  \__,_|___\___/|___/___/_|  \___/

  AIOSCPU - AI Operating System  (OS-SHELL mode)
  © 2026 Chris Betts | AIOSCPU Official | AI-generated, fully legal
============================================================
AIOSCPU - OS-SHELL mode: standard multi-user login
============================================================
